---
import BaseLayout from "../components/layout/base-layout.astro";
import SectionHeader from "../components/ui/section-header.astro";
import Stat from "../components/ui/stat.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Anthony Lupo" description="Eight years of B2B SaaS sales, AI tools, and building systems.">
  <section class="container page">
    <SectionHeader
      overline="About"
      title="The full story"
    />

    <div class="narrative prose-width">
      <p class="lead">
        I'm a customer-focused professional who lives at the intersection of sales,
        technical thinking, and genuine curiosity. Over eight years in B2B SaaS I've
        learned that the best deals come from actually understanding what a customer
        is trying to solve, not just what they say they want to buy.
      </p>

      <h3>Salesforce (2015-2019)</h3>
      <p>
        Salesforce is where I learned how to sell. Started as an SDR and led the
        org of 43 in ACV eight out of eleven months. Moved into Enterprise
        Business Development focused on Oil and Gas, hitting 130% attainment.
        Then into an AE role with Health Cloud.
      </p>

      <h3>Samsara (2019-2020)</h3>
      <p>
        The hardest professional experience I've had, and one of the most important.
        Put on a PIP within my first months. Hit 250% of quota during the PIP.
        Drove 300% ARR growth year over year through a strategic shift to mid-enterprise.
      </p>

      <h3>Yext (2020-2025)</h3>
      <p>
        Five years is where I figured out what kind of seller I actually am. Came in
        as a mid-market AE and left as a Principal AE managing 15 accounts at $700M
        to $1B ARR each. Hit Presidents Club, mentored 5 reps, posted a 245% quarter,
        and built systems the broader team adopted.
      </p>

      <h3>What I'm after</h3>
      <p>
        A role where sales experience, technical curiosity, and the ability to simplify
        complexity come together. Ideally at an AI-forward company building something
        ambitious.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-section">
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <Stat value="245%" label="Peak quarter (Yext Q2)" />
        <Stat value="$558K" label="Largest deal (Good Feet)" />
        <Stat value="130%" label="Enterprise BDR attainment" />
        <Stat value="#1" label="SDR ACV rank (8/11 months)" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    padding-top: var(--space-24);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .narrative {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .narrative h3 {
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
  }

  .narrative p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .stats-section {
    padding-top: var(--space-12);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-default);
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-6);
    }
  }
</style>
